        {
            "title": "川普呼籲以直接支付取代歐巴馬健保",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ae3OCk7O4eJ3aGUyWhp_pA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_3_M_1440048334.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com — 美國總統川普表示,應廢除《平價醫療法案》(Affordable Care Act),改以直接向個人支付款項的制度取代,而非透過保險公司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在Truth Social上發文批評他所謂的「負擔不起的醫療法案」(Unaffordable Care Act),主張資金應直接發放給美國民眾,讓他們自行購買醫療保險,而非依賴保險公司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他補充表示,目前的制度難以為繼,並重申他長期以來的立場,即歐巴馬健保應由更以消費者為導向的模式取代。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-048eb2a7-41fe-34af-afa8-b44aa94f7d82-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普的最新言論可能對健康保險公司造成負面影響,包括聯合健康集團(NYSE:UNH)、Elevance Health Inc(NYSE:ELV)、CVS Health Corp(NYSE:CVS)、Centene Corp(NYSE:CNC)及Humana Inc(NYSE:HUM),當市場於週一重新開盤時。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E4%BB%A5%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E6%AD%90%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E5%81%A5%E4%BF%9D-145938582.html",
